ROBERT J. BLACK, ESQ.

Email: RBlack@Welbaum.com

Mr. Black was born and raised in Miami, Florida. He has extensive legal experience having continuously practiced law in Miami-Dade County for over forty years. Not only has Mr. Black been active representing clients for their legal matters but he has been involved in many legal and civic organizations.
